EA Sports Nhl statistics Scraper

Summary:
 - eanhlstats: python module to fetch and parse team & player stats from easports servers. (append to PYTHONPATH)
 - pyfibot_module: module for pyfibot irc bot (http://code.google.com/p/pyfibot/), which uses nhlstatsparse package.

Bot commands: 
 .ts <team name>: Show Team Stats for team (always fetched from server)
 .ps <player_name@team>: show player stats from a specific team. Within single request data is cached for 5 minutes for the whole team, making following requests from the same team faster. 
 .switch: Switch between PS3 and Xbox 360 mode (can only fetch data from one at a time)

Check examples about how to use this thing from tests.	
Run tests with specloud tests.py

Define in eanhlstats.settings whether you are interested in PS3 or XBX statistics.

Requirements:
 - Peewee
 - BeautifulSoup
 
 Dev:
 - Specloud
 - Mock